v0.25.0: cartoon pounce + comic-impact kill

- mid-dart, predators stretch forward, squash down, spring into a little pounce arc and lean into the dive (classic squash-and-stretch)
- a successful kill triggers a punchy scale-pop on the predator and a bright white/orange 'POW' star-burst at the strike point (grey poof for the prey still plays too)
- kill impact flows through a new context.burst() channel + world event type 2
